### Warning #2 ‚Äî Experimental Profile

This Wasteland profile is **experimental**.

That said:
- I have personally playtested the delivered profile  
- No errors appeared  
- No concerning warnings appeared  
- Several hours of gameplay were stable  

Still, this is provided **as-is**.

---

### Warning #3 ‚Äî This Profile Is Fragile

This is the most important section.

The normal Sm√∂rg√•sbord profile can tolerate a lot of mod toggling during a new game.  
**The Wasteland profile cannot.**

> Consider this MO2 profile to be **extremely fragile**.

#### Safe:
- You can **disable** mods you don‚Äôt want, and the profile will usually continue to function.

#### Unsafe:
- Enabling additional mods is very likely to break things.
- Mods touching any of the following are especially risky:
  - UI  
  - Progression  
  - Recipes  
  - Traders  
  - Loot  
  - Armor  
  - Weapons  

> Enabling even a single incompatible mod can introduce errors.

